1
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:03,120
One, ten, hundred, thousand, ten thousand, hundred thousand, million.

2
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,240
Oh, my God.

3
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,360
It's an instant kill.

4
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,640
Shengtian Banzi held the top for so many days.

5
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,370
He was overtaken in an instant.

6
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,040
This is the world of the rich.

7
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,880
Why are you watching this kind of stuff too?

8
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,010
Where is Liang Chen?

9
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:27,840
Did he not come?

10
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,360
It's already been two days.

11
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,640
I only chose this course for him.

12
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,840
Donghai 183 sent a rocket.

13
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:44,200
Sigh, I still lost.

14
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:51,440
Let me check on the fans in the stream.

15
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:56,079
Wow, what's going on?

16
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:59,440
Can someone tell me what's happening?

17
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,880
Thank you all for the gifts.

18
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,560
That's it for today's stream.

19
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,320
Bye.

20
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,480
What's wrong?

21
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:25,520
I've been streaming for so long.

22
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,880
I've never seen such random gifting.

23
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,240
It is indeed unusual.

24
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,120
And,

25
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,840
most of it was sent by Donghai 183.

26
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:36,160
He's sent almost a million points.

27
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,880
He just entered the room.

28
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,760
Could it be someone I know?

29
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,240
Who exactly is this person?

30
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,400
Who is this top donor?

31
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,520
Such a spendthrift.

32
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,320
Zixi.

33
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,360
Actually,

34
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,040
I'm the top donor.

35
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,040
After luckily becoming

36
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:57,240
your 10,000th fan,

37
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,200
I felt like we were

38
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,840
destined for each other.

39
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,200
What?

40
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:11,840
The one topping the chart is Liang Chen.

41
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,800
Why?

42
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,680
What makes Yin Zixi deserve this?

43
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,120
I did a rough calculation.

44
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,839
Around hundreds of thousands have been spent.

45
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,839
What?

46
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,680
Keep your voice down, girl.

47
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,400
Who exactly is Donghai 183?

48
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,740
Why is the recent diary always a step behind?

49
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,880
Can't I get a little cheat code?

50
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:34,600
Still not satisfied?

51
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,560
Wen Lingli.

52
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,240
Finally caught you,

53
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,570
big influencer.

54
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,490
What do you want from me?

55
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,760
I heard you sing and dance in your live stream.

56
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,440
You are very popular among those lonely men.

57
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,440
My interaction with my fans,

58
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,400
why do you make it sound so disgusting?

59
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,280
Whether it's disgusting or not,

60
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,680
you know it in your heart.

61
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,840
What do you mean?

62
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,159
What exactly did you do to Liang Chen?

63
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,880
I didn't do anything to him.

64
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:03,040
Then why did he spend hundreds of thousands to support you?

65
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,720
He spent hundreds of thousands on me?

66
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,250
You're still playing dumb.

67
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,800
Wen Lingli.

68
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,840
Are you crazy?

69
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:12,940
Liang Chen,

70
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,840
are you bewitched?

71
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,960
What's wrong with you today?

72
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:24,440
Huh?

73
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,120
Oh.

74
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,960
Nothing.

75
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:29,120
You seem to be out of it.

76
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,560
Donghai 183

77
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,680
seems to be Liang Chen from our class.

78
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,000
Liang Chen?

79
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:36,800
Yeah.

80
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,320
Senior,

81
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,280
I want to return the money to him.

82
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,159
Are you sure it's him?

83
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,480
I...

84
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:58,640
Who do you think told Wen Lingli?

85
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,160
Yeah,

86
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:02,640
that person really has a big mouth.

87
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,040
Hao.

88
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,080
Do you think I

89
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:08,580
did a bad thing with good intentions?

90
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,080
Boss.

91
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,000
If there are such bad things in the future,

92
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,240
come to me first.

93
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:17,320
Zixi wasn't happy at all.

94
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,280
Really?

95
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,840
Didn't you watch her stream?

96
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,560
She didn't smile.

97
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:26,240
She used to smile a lot.

98
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,840
You've only watched his livestream twice, right?

99
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,929
What did you say?

100
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:36,440
I said, you've only watched twice.

101
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:38,200
You want me to tell her directly?

102
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,720
I never said that.

103
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,280
That makes sense.

104
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,920
Casting Deputy Director: Xi Chongjing

105
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,840
Props Assistant: Li Kunxiao

106
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,760
Production Vehicle: Yi Mingle

107
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:24,720
Yitong
